OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften cloudy with a little
OL,6,Fdrizzle in places this morning,
OL,7,Flargely over higher ground, although
OL,8,Fmany places staying dry. More
OL,9,Fpersistent and sometimes heavy rain
OL,10,Farriving from the west during the
OL,11,Fafternoon, and turning windier.
OL,12,FAnother mild day.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain continuing to spread
OL,15,Feast this evening giving a generally
OL,16,Fwet night, although the rain perhaps
OL,17,Feasing a little later. Rather windy on
OL,18,Fsouthern coasts and breezy inland.
OL,19,FVery mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
