OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA damp start with some drizzly
OL,6,Frain. Perhaps turning somewhat
OL,7,Fbrighter by the afternoon, but a risk
OL,8,Fof heavy showers. Breezy, and possibly
OL,9,Fwindy later in some exposed areas.
OL,10,FMild.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FAfter
OL,13,Fa chilly start, becoming mostly fine
OL,14,Fon Saturday with some sunshine.
OL,15,FTurning damp and windy on Sunday.
OL,16,FBrighter on Monday, but with showers
OL,17,Farriving from the west. Staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
